ğŸ”¹ Program 7: Convert String to Uppercase

#include <stdio.h>
#include <ctype.h>

int main() {
    char str[100];
    printf("Enter a string: ");
    fgets(str, sizeof(str), stdin);

    for (int i = 0; str[i] != '\0'; i++) {
        str[i] = toupper(str[i]);
    }
    printf("Uppercase string: %s", str);
    return 0;
}
ğŸ”¸ Sample Input: Enter a string: Hello World
ğŸ”¸ Sample Output: Uppercase string: HELLO WORLD





